<b>Capcom Selling Stock</b> - Bumper 13:48 pm 09-27-00
</table></div>

<div class=itemtext>
From SegaWeb...<P>  <I>Speaking of Capcom and army of robot developers, the company has announced they'll be offering the chance to snatch up some stock. Beginning October 4, 4.7 million shares of previously privately held Capcom stock will be available on the Tokyo Stock Exchange. The price of the stock is expected to be announced sometime between October 2 and October 6. </I><P>  Credit: <A HREF="http://segaweb.com/news/0900/102.html">SegaWeb News Bytes</A><br>
